ation:\nIf the grieving person prefers not to engage in external support, it's understandable. However, it's also important to offer resources and options that align with their values and needs.\n\n### Cognitive Engagement Ratings:\nA: 8\nV: 9\nG: 7\nP: 6\nE: 5\nQ: 4\nC: 3\nY: 2\nF: 1\nD: 0\n\n### Contextual Awareness:\nNavigating the grieving process requires flexibility and adaptability. It's important to remain open to different approaches and to listen actively to the individual's concerns.\n\n### Query Interpretation:\nIn cases where the grieving person does not want external support,",
